{
  "slug": "queues-turn-spikes-into-lines",
  "title": "Queues turn spikes into lines",
  "category": "tech",
  "kicker": "Distributed systems",
  "hook": "A queue does not make work disappear. It makes work wait in a place you can observe.",
  "readMinutes": 5,
  "date": "2026-06-23",
  "tags": [
    "queues",
